        "2c7496d4-aa34-42d8-8337-67257e0fefe6": {
          "v": "v1",
          "flow": {
            "raw": [
              {
                "id": "1",
                "cid": [
                  "2-1",
                  "2-2"
                ],
                "pid": [],
                "title": "",
                "content": "<p>千咲：怎么了，漂泊者？为什么突然回头？</p>"
              },
              {
                "id": "2-1",
                "cid": [
                  "3-1"
                ],
                "pid": [
                  "1"
                ],
                "group": "2",
                "title": "刚才，收音机里传出来了一个声音。",
                "content": "<p>千咲：一个声音？收音机不是已经坏掉了吗？</p>",
                "delEdgeChildren": []
              },
              {
                "id": "2-2",
                "cid": [
                  "3-1"
                ],
                "pid": [
                  "1"
                ],
                "group": "2",
                "title": "好像有人在叫我的名字。",
                "content": "<p>千咲：有吗？我就在你边上，但&hellip;&hellip;我没听见？</p>",
                "delEdgeChildren": []
              },
              {
                "id": "3-1",
                "cid": [
                  "4-1",
                  "4-2"
                ],
                "pid": [
                  "2-1",
                  "2-2"
                ],
                "group": "3",
                "title": "所以……你没听到奇怪的声音？",
                "content": "<p>千咲：&hellip;&hellip;嗯。你是不是有点累了？我们先回咖啡厅休息？</p>",
                "delEdgeChildren": []
              },
              {
                "id": "4-1",
                "cid": [
                  "5-1"
                ],
                "pid": [
                  "3-1"
                ],
                "group": "4",
                "title": "好，确实该歇一歇了。",
                "content": "",
                "delEdgeChildren": []
              },
              {
                "id": "4-2",
                "cid": [
                  "5-1"
                ],
                "pid": [
                  "3-1"
                ],
                "group": "4",
                "title": "别担心，我没事。",
                "content": "",
                "delEdgeChildren": []
              },
              {
                "id": "5-1",
                "cid": [],
                "pid": [
                  "4-1",
                  "4-2"
                ],
                "group": "5",
                "title": "",
                "content": "<p>漂泊者：（但是，刚才听到的那些话&hellip;&hellip;不像是简单的幻听。）</p>",
                "delEdgeChildren": []
              }
            ],
            "data": {},
            "structure": {
              "id": "1"
            },
            "individual": []
          },
          "title": "",
          "branch": "1",
          "content": "",
